There are no words that can do justice to how I feel right now. 

I have dreamed of this moment for as long as I can remember. This is just the beginning though and I hope I continue to do you all proud! 

Firstly I want to thank everyone at @lagalaxy . You will always be in my heart. 

Also Stockton @tlj.fc for the constant love and support. Stockton will always be home. 

To Gabriel & Luis at @ocelot_sports , none of this wouldve been possible without you guys. Thanks for believing in me and lets get it!

To MCFC, Miguel and especially to Gary, thank you for giving me this opportunity, I will not let you down. 

Lastly, there is no thank you big enough to give my parents and family. Dad, you have always done everything to support and train me and mom you have always been there at my side when I need you.

I love you guys, thank you for letting me chase my dreams.

Happy to be here, let’s get to work. Muchas gracias a todos por el apoyo!!!! 💪🏼⚽️
